{"tid":2158748,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國國防部停止對本港警隊等提供培訓","createTime":"2020-08-16T01:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T02:20:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7dd2f0a8d9f9a1a90b87db4caa24a5cfd8d619b","tid":2158748,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T01:59:24.000Z","msg":"英國《觀察家報》引述國防部的消息報道，英國政府因應中英關係惡化，加上新型肺炎的疫情，決定暫停安排陸軍及空軍為香港警隊、政府飛行服務隊及香港海事青年團，提供培訓，現時留待疫情過後，再檢討是否繼續進行培訓的合約。<br />\n<br />\n英國國防部發言人表示，英國政府已經明確指出，中國在香港實施的「港區國安法」，違反《中英聯合聲明》，直接威脅港人的權利及自由，加上疫情的影響，決定暫停培訓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543960-20200816.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543960-20200816.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELx68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=974e9725\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543960-20200816.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5cb949b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543960-20200816.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6158fc8b68348ffdf906562f7771b7658a57f558","tid":2158748,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba32a45b97de271f0dde0370e94aaa3b4ea7292b","tid":2158748,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"英國國防部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28c12b4aa66618e0f3c00d435e2a73a3059794a","tid":2158748,"uid":143241,"